{"word":"G1578 - ἐκκλίνω - ekklínō - ek-klee'-no - Avoid","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκκλίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ekklínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ek-klee'-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Avoid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விட்டுவிலகு, வழிதப்பு, விட்டு நீங்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to turn (oneself) away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G2827 - κλίνω - klínō - klee'-no/2827\">G2827</a>; to <i>deviate</i>, that is, (absolutely) to <i>shun</i> (literally or figuratively), or (relatively) to <i>decline</i> (from piety): - avoid, eschew, go out of the way."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}